title: Kaduva
subTitle: Kaduva pledges to seek revenge against IG Joseph when the police officer sends Kaduva to jail and torments his loved ones.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Uvaa
subTitle: Five teenagers, who lead a carefree life, face challenges at their new convent school. Although their intentions are purely romantic, a horrifying event threatens to change their lives forever.

title: Mickey Virus
subTitle: When the woman he loves regrets a web transaction, a hacker decides to help her undo it. However, chaos ensues when he accidentally commits a robbery instead.

subTitle: Next-door neighbours Vidyadhar, an orthodox Hindu man, and Mehak, an urban dancer, cannot stand each other. However, they must live together when their apartments get raided.

subTitle: A parking spot frays the relationship between two neighbours of different generations and world views. Soon, the two men find themselves in an escalating battle to have the space all to themselves.

title: Balloon
subTitle: Jeevanand rents an old house in Ooty with his wife and nephew hoping to find inspiration to write a script. However, strange events begin unfolding in the house which are linked to his past.

title: Kee
subTitle: Siddharth, a hacker who is blessed with a happy family, falls in love with a girl. However, his life changes drastically when he becomes a victim of cyberbullying that leads him to another hacker.

title: Boss
subTitle: Disowned by his father as a boy, Surya seeks protection from a crime boss. When his brother is wrongfully sent to prison, his father begs him to intervene.

title: L7
subTitle: Arun and Sandhya, a newly married couple, move into a new home to begin their marital life. However, Arun soon realises that his wife is possessed and he must do whatever it takes to save her.

title: Golmaal Again
subTitle: Five orphan men return to the orphanage they grew up in to attend their mentor's funeral. However, they encounter the ghost of their childhood friend, Khushi, and help her attain salvation.

title: Junga
subTitle: Junga, a simple bus conductor, lives with his mother and learns that his father lost their ancestral property to Chettiyar. However, he soon turns to the life of crime to retrieve it.

subTitle: The chief minister's passing wreaks havoc across the state and in his political party. However, a mysterious contender for the post rises to eradicate wrongdoers.

title: Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior
subTitle: Tanhaji, a Maratha warrior, is Shivaji Maharaj's trusted lieutenant. When the Mughals invade and conquer Kondhana fort, he sets out to reclaim it for his king and country.

title: Anwar

title: Filler
